text: This area has a long history. It situated near alot of low rise buildings. An area which also comprises of both residential and commercial shop houses. The popular Chinatown of wet market and food area is along the stretch of pathway.
A peaceful stretch of greenery sanwiched between the commercial shophouses.
Morning sun. Good for strolling and photo taking.
It is a long promenade park that runs through the middle of the city from Chinatown to Tanjong Pagar. I loved taking a walk in the morning, buying coffee at a nearby cafe, and taking a break here.
